            <div type="edition" xml:space="preserve"><head>Text</head><ab><lb n="1"/>
                Divo Vero <expan><abbr>Parth</abbr><ex>ico</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>max</abbr><ex>imo</ex></expan> fratri <lb n="2"/><expan><abbr>Imp</abbr><ex>eratoris</ex></expan> Caesaris <expan><abbr>M</abbr><ex>arci</ex></expan> Aureli <expan><abbr>Antonin</abbr><ex>i</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>Aug</abbr><ex>usti</ex></expan> <lb n="3"/><expan><abbr>Armeniac</abbr><ex>i</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>Medic</abbr><ex>i</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>Germ</abbr><ex>anici</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>Parthic</abbr><ex>i</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>max</abbr><ex>imi</ex></expan> <lb n="4"/><expan><abbr>tribunic</abbr><ex>iae</ex></expan> potestatis XXVI <expan><abbr>imp</abbr><ex>eratoris</ex></expan> V <expan><abbr>p</abbr><ex>atris</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>p</abbr><ex>atriae</ex></expan> <lb n="5"/>co<expan><ex>n</ex><abbr>s</abbr><ex>ulis</ex></expan> III proco<expan><ex>n</ex><abbr>s</abbr><ex>ulis</ex></expan> <lb n="6"/>colonia Ulpia <expan><abbr>Traian</abbr><ex>a</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>Aug</abbr><ex>usta</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>Dac</abbr><ex>ica</ex></expan> <lb n="7"/>Sarmizegetusa
            </ab></div>
            <div type="commentary">
                <p>Nach Piso stammt die Tafel vom Forum Vetus in Sarmizegetusa.</p>
            </div>
